title: VMO on the Track - an instrumental mixtape (TPB Edition)
description:
VMOmedia presents: "VMO on the Track - an instrumental mixtape"

This is an instrumental mixtape that I released for free back in 2012, figured I might as well throw it on one of my favorite sites. All of these instrumentals are free for non-commercial use, I only ask that you contact me if you'd like to learn more about commercial licensing.

Find more by me and consider supporting my music if you like it at the following locations:

All of the included MP3s are 320kbps, WAVs can be released upon request. Shitty album art included, too.

I'm interested to see what people think, so feedback is always welcome! Please seed, as I won't be able to forever
